5. CLOUD SERVICES AND API ACCESS
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The Software interacts with DAL Technology's proprietary backend services,
including but not limited to: peer discovery relay, message relay, location
services, push notification delivery, and points-of-interest data aggregation.

  (a) These services are operated solely for the benefit of authorised Radar
      app users and are not a public API.

  (b) All API requests are authenticated with cryptographic keys and anti-replay
      mechanisms. Attempting to forge, replicate, or spoof authentication
      credentials is strictly prohibited.

  (c) DAL Technology reserves the right to suspend or terminate API access,
      without notice or liability, to any device or user found to be in breach
      of this Agreement.

  (d) You acknowledge that your device's IP address, UUID, and request metadata
      are logged for security, abuse prevention, and operational purposes in
      accordance with our Privacy Policy.


